race.comment: DOUBT IN THE SKY (8) finished third last time over 1000m at Bairnsdale when resuming from a spell, beaten half a length. Will trim down second-up. In the mix. KENTUCKY WOMEN (4) finished second last start at the first run back from a spell over 1200m at Bairnsdale, beaten a long neck. Needs to be at her best to beat this field but she cannot be ruled out. HELL OF A GENT (2) settled well back then made some inroads and finished 1.4 lengths away in fourth last time out over 975m at Swan Hill when fresh from a spell. Steps up in distance today. Sure to run well. PUNIC WAR (3) comes here second-up after a sound performance fresh. This looks a more suitable race for him today and he's expected to be in the finish.
